Author: TheCarbdashian
Text: That probably means he cares about you. I know that in a lot of households, people will show their ultimate affection by feeding the ones they love. I had friends whose families were from Mexico and, NGL, a lot of them were chonky. But God dammit once I had her mother's cooking I completely understood why.   At this point, any gain is probably just from the food itself. I wouldn't worry too much. :)
